  "text": "The additional segmentation is done in order to refine the previous speaker segmentation output and to remove irrelevant speakers (i.e. speakers with a low number of assigned frames). In this case the algorithm creates a new HMM models generated from the previous segmentation output and then applying an iterative speaker model training/Viterbi decoding loop [CITATION_1] .",
